      public double startProcess()
      Basic analysis workflow. Manages the process of sentiment analysis on input data using a lexicon. The overall time complexity will depend on the most complex operation in its implementation. Since file reading and sentiment analysis are performed linearly, the overall complexity is also O(n) without taking into account constant factors and terms.
